If you have any suggests I am happy to add them to the list.

for 0.2 release
    - core
        - add plugin api version check ... see doc/plugin-api
        - install the wmii.3lua man page in ~/.wmii-3.5
        - 'man' action that will launch an xterm displaying wmii.3lua page

    - bundled plugins
        - 'browser' and 'google' actions to go to a browser

for 0.3 release
    - core
        - rewrite timer handling using select loop and coroutines 
          and a subprocess to do iread() ... see doc/event-loop
        - support for "raw mode" like win-space in wmii+ruby
        - add wmii.load_plugin("name") which works harder to locate a
          plugin file

    - bundled plugins
        - mpd: controls / volume
        - acpi: battery life / thermal
        - cpufreq: cpu freq / governor
        - whereami: wireless / controls

